Package: generalKSStat
Type: Package
Title: Computes Goodness-of-Fit Test Statistics Such as the 
    Kolmogorov-Smirnov, Berk-Jones and the Higher Criticism Statistics
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2020-02-17
Author: Jiefei Wang
Maintainer: Jiefei Wang<jwang96@buffalo.edu>
Description: Computing goodness-of-fit test statistics and their p-values
    using the Exact-KS-FFT method developed by Dimitrova, Kaishev, Tan (2017). 
    The algorithm works for the sample size up to 25,000.
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: C++11
